FBIS4-15124 "drsov067_h_94001" FBIS-SOV-94-067 Daily Report 1 Apr 1994 Moldova Tiraspol Militiamen Join Military Militia Battalion Tiraspol Militiamen Join Military Militia Battalion AU0704082094 Chisinau BASAPRESS in English 1857 GMT 1 Apr 94 AU0704082094 Chisinau BASAPRESS English BFN [Text] Tiraspol, BASAPRESS, 1/4/1994 -- Informed sources from the Russian Defense Ministry told BASAPRESS that is has been recently decided to create a military militia battalion comprising several hundreds people in the 14th Army. The former Tiraspol militiamen are now joining the battalion. According to local observers, the force used by the Dniester ministries of interior and security as well as the difference in salaries made many people quit the Ministry of Interior and join this battalion.
